    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 981-generation Cayman S, an analog masterpiece in concours condition. This mid-engine icon is powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and an integrated dry-sump lubrication system. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides crisp, short-throw engagement, complemented by the Sport Chrono package for active powertrain mounts and rev-matching. This example features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), lowering the ride height by 10mm for sharpened turn-in and lateral stability. The undercarriage is spotless, with no oxidation on the aluminum subframes or suspension components. Rolling on 20-inch Carrera S alloys with fresh N-spec rubber, the braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers with zero rotor lip. Documentation is exhaustive, including a clean DME overrev report and full service logs.",
      "price": 48500.0,
