    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014this beauty is a total dream! It's been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Spotless inside and out, it drives like a dream and has been kept in pristine shape. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership stress, you\u2019ve found it! Come see it for yourself\u2014you're going to love it! \u2728",
