    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a definitive example of mechanical purity, featuring the highly desirable 3.8L 9A1 flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring and longitudinal grip. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing a lowered ride height and adaptive damping that remains factory-spec tight. This vehicle exhibits zero bore scoring concerns and features an immaculate undercarriage with no oxidation on the suspension pick-up points or exhaust manifold. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
